<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:KaiTi_GB2312;font-size:24px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:KaiTi_GB2312;font-size:18px;\"></span></strong> </strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:KaiTi_GB2312;font-size:24px;\"><br />\r\n</span></strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<a href=\"/detail/83.html\" target=\"_blank\"></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:KaiTi_GB2312;font-size:24px;\"><strong> </strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-family:KaiTi_GB2312;font-size:24px;\"><br />\r\n</span> </strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-family:KaiTi_GB2312;font-size:24px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n</span> </strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n</strong>', '', '11', '1');
INSERT INTO `xiaobing360_category` VALUES ('82', '', '安防监控工程', '', '5', '5', '1', '10', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'page_tongyong', '', '5', '2,3,7', '4', '0', '1', '1', '0', '0', '', '', '1493796091', '1495589511', '1', '0', '0', '0', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:FangSong_GB2312;font-size:16px;\"><b>系统概述</b></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:FangSong_GB2312;font-size:16px;\">监控系统由摄像、传输、存储显示3大部分组成。前端摄像机通过视频线缆将视频图像传输到控制主机，控制主机再将视频型号分配到相应监视器及录像设备，同时可将需要传输的语音信号同步录入到主机内。通过控制主机，操作人员可发出指令，对云台进行控制、对镜头进行调焦变倍的操作，并可通过控制主机实现在多路摄像机之间的切换。利用特殊的录像处理模式，可对图像进行录入、回放、处理等操作，使录像效果达到最佳。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/Websites/zhongyu/Uploads/Editor/2017-05-03/59098534b2c70.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"justify\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#666666;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;\">\r\n		<b><span style=\"font-family:FangSong_GB2312;font-size:16px;\">系统设备组成</span></b><b></b>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"justify\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#666666;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:FangSong_GB2312;font-size:16px;\">视频监控系统产品包含光端机，光缆终端盒、云台、云台解码器、视频矩阵、硬盘录像机、监控摄像头、镜头、支架。视频监控系统组成部分包含监控前端、管理中心、监控中心、</span><span style=\"font-family:FangSong_GB2312;font-size:16px;\">PC客户端及无线网桥。各组成部分的说明如下：</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"justify\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;margin-left:0pt;color:#666666;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;text-align:justify;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:FangSong_GB2312;font-size:16px;\">1．监控前端：用于采集被监控点的监控信息，并可以配备报警设备。</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"justify\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;margin-left:42pt;color:#666666;font-size:14px;text-indent:0pt;text-align:justify;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:FangSong_GB2312;font-size:16px;\">a.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:FangSong_GB2312;font-size:16px;\">普通摄像机</span><span style=\"font-family:FangSong_GB2312;font-size:16px;\">+视频服务器。普通摄像机可以是模拟摄像机，也可以是数字摄像机。原始视频信号传到视频服务器，经视频服务器编码后，以TCP/IP协议通过网络传至其他设备。</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"justify\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;margin-left:42pt;color:#666666;font-size:14px;text-indent:0pt;text-align:justify;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:FangSong_GB2312;font-size:16px;\">b.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:FangSong_GB2312;font-size:16px;\">网络摄像机。网络摄像机是融摄像、视频编码</span><span style=\"font-family:FangSong_GB2312;font-size:16px;\">Web服务于一体的高级摄像设备，内嵌了TCP/IP协议通过网络传至其他设备。</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"justify\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;margin-left:0pt;color:#666666;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;text-align:justify;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:FangSong_GB2312;font-size:16px;\">2．管理中心：承担所有前端设备的管理、控制、报警处理、录像回放、用户管理等工作。各部分功能分别由专门的服务器各司其职。</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"justify\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;margin-left:0pt;color:#666666;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;text-align:justify;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:FangSong_GB2312;font-size:16px;\">3．监控中心：用于集中对所辖区域进行监控，包括电视墙、监控客户终端群组成。系统中可以有一个或多个监控中心。</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"justify\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;margin-left:0pt;color:#666666;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;text-align:justify;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:FangSong_GB2312;font-size:16px;\">4．PC客户端：在监控中心之外，也可以由PC机接到网络上进行远程监控。</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"justify\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;margin-left:0pt;color:#666666;font-size:14px;text-indent:24pt;text-align:justify;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:FangSong_GB2312;font-size:16px;\">5．</span><span style=\"font-family:FangSong_GB2312;font-size:16px;\">无线网桥：无线网桥用于接入无线数据网络，并访问互联网。通过无线网桥，可以将</span><span style=\"font-family:FangSong_GB2312;font-size:16px;\">IP网上的监控信息传至无线终端，也可以将无线终端的控制指令传给IP网上的视频监控管理系统。常用的无线网桥为CDMA网络。</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#666666;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:FangSong_GB2312;font-size:16px;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"justify\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#666666;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;\">\r\n		<b><span style=\"font-family:FangSong_GB2312;font-size:16px;\">礼行实力</span></b><b></b>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"justify\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#666666;font-size:14px;text-align:justify;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:FangSong_GB2312;font-size:16px;\">1.良好的行业信誉（已合作过的客户，对我司的专业服务有着极高的评价）；</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:FangSong_GB2312;font-size:16px;\">2.公司拥有一支专业化高效迅速的安装维护、维修队伍；</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:FangSong_GB2312;font-size:16px;\">3.设备厂家的技术支持；</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:FangSong_GB2312;font-size:16px;\">全方位满足客户需求，为客户提供高质量高标准的专业化监控系统安装服务。</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', '', '11', '1');
INSERT INTO `xiaobing360_category` VALUES ('5', '', '网络工程', '', '0', '5', '2', '50', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'page_message', '', '0', '2,3', '5', '0', '1', '1', '0', '0', '', '', '1464941879', '1495591663', '1', '0', '0', '18', '', '<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', 'page/82', '20', '1');
INSERT INTO `xiaobing360_category` VALUES ('7', '', '电力', '', '2', '2', '2', '10', '', '', '随着国内高净值人士的持续增长，国人的海外投资欲望与强大的购买力正撬动着全球的楼市。目前，越来越多的对海外房产有着浓厚兴趣的中国投资者们已经走出国门，置业全球。海外房产投资有着买房不限贷、永久产权、自由买卖等优势。当国内的楼市不再满足中国高净值人群和精英人事的投资要求时，我们开始把目光投向了海外，通过全球资产配置为投资人的人生、事业、家庭、未来进行全面筹划。', '', '', '', 'page_tongyong', '', '5', '2,3,7', '4', '0', '1', '1', '0', '0', '', '', '1464944474', '1495589517', '1', '0', '345', '0', '', '<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">2000年以来，电力行业增长速度远高于前20年平均增速。工业化、城镇化、市场化、国际化共同促进了电力工业的快速发展。随着电力行业业务量的连续增长，为适应市场需求，电力行业资产投入也在不断加大，在专业生产设备不断投入的同时，IT资产的投入也在迅速扩大。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n	但是，目前整个电力行业的信息技术建设还缺乏统一性标准，管理效率低下，在安全防范、设备监控等方面存在许多隐患。\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	首先，电力行业数据中心内各种设备类型复杂，地域分布广，人工维护困难。其次，为适应减员增效和现代化管理的要求，对管理系统在可靠性、易用性及易维护性上，尤其对远程集中管理方面提出了更高的要求。\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	提供统一管理平台、确保系统的安全稳定可靠、提高工作效率，这些需求在海康为电力行业打造的多项具体解决方案应用上都得到了很好的体现。\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	电力监控应用\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	应用案例：上海XX第二电厂。\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	使用设备：海康SV1108。\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.huimaidz.com/uploads/allimg/150429/1-1504291625595V.jpg\" style=\"width:447px;height:225px;\" /> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	控制台可以操控其下任意一台DVR，将电视墙上任意一个画面切换至控制台进行接管，切换方式方便快捷；通过操作可以支持下载、备份当前被接管的DVR录像资料至USB存储设备，而无需将存储设备分别接入不同硬盘录像机来进行下载、备份；可及时近距离地查找发现视频中异常画面。另外，通过控制台的鼠标可控制当前被接管的DVR内嵌软件，包括支持按时间段、监控点检索、回放录像资料等，单台画面数切换。\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', 'http://maikesi.hk182.so313.com/lists/2.html', '11', '1');
INSERT INTO `xiaobing360_category` VALUES ('53', '', '网络工程', '', '3', '3', '4', '10', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'page_tongyong', '', '5', '2,3,7', '4', '0', '1', '1', '0', '0', '', '', '1473303133', '1494839776', '1', '0', '0', '0', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-left:0cm;color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:center;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:18px;\"><strong>英国</strong></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:18px;\"><strong>200</strong></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:18px;\"><strong>万英镑投资移民</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-left:0cm;color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:center;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;世界金融中心、经济强国、名校云集的英国一直是广大高资产人士向往之地，</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">11</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">日起英国开始实施新的投资移民政策。在新政策下，操作模式更加规范，投资范围更加明确，更加入了优惠条款，即使投资发生亏损也无需补仓。投资期满后返还投资款。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:center;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\"><img src=\"/Websites/zhongyu/Uploads/Editor/2016-07-27/579852ad68de1.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:center;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;color:#E56600;\"><strong>一、投资期限</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 投资</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">200</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">万英镑，投资期五年</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 投资</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">500</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">万英镑，投资期三年</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 投资</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">1000</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">万英镑，投资期两年</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;color:#E56600;\"><strong>二、申请条件</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1、主申请人年满</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">18</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">周岁，无任何刑事犯罪记录；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2、在英国监管银行储存可支配的自有资金不少于两百万英镑；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 3、意愿全部投资英国国债、股票或公司债券。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;color:#E56600;\"><strong>三、项目优势</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;1、欧洲最发达的国家之一，世界金融中心之一，资本市场成熟及发达。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2、生活环境及质量高，社会治安良好，高度法治，尊重人权，保护私产。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;3、 申请资料简单，无需证明资金来源及税单，无需管理经验、商业背景、年龄、学历、语言要求；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;4、 办理周期短，申请简单快捷，</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">4-6</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">个月即可获批；</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;5</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">年以后转永居。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;5、英国教育举世闻名，</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">16</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">岁以下子女可享受免费或以低廉学费享一流纯正英式高等教育。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;6、全家（主申请人和配偶及</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">18</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">岁以下未婚子女）可一起获取英国身份，入境后享受英国优厚福利；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;7、主申请人满足居住要求，可保全家身份有效，获取永居后再无居住要求；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;8、英国讲诚信，政府</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">AAA</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">级国债无投资风险。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;color:#E56600;\"><strong>四、居住要求</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1、首次获得</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">年的签证，</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">年后再续签</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">年，主申请人需于</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">年内每年在英国住满半年，</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">年后可获永久居留，第</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">年可申请入籍；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2、获得永居后，每</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">年仅需入境英国一次。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;color:#E56600;\"><strong>五、备注：另可选择</strong></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;color:#E56600;\"><strong>40</strong></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;color:#E56600;\"><strong>万英镑融资贷款模式</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"color:#535353;line-height:28px;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\"></span><span style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;line-height:28px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\"></span><span style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;line-height:28px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\"></span> \r\n<p style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:center;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\"><img src=\"/Websites/zhongyu/Uploads/Editor/2016-07-27/579852d9be6a5.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span> \r\n</p>', '', '11', '1');
