aHei\';font-size:16px;\">可达；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;The University of Melbourme</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">（墨尔本大学）和</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">RMIT</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">（墨尔本皇家理工学院），MONARC项目前</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">6条线路</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">的电车直达这两个大学。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:center;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/Websites/zhongyu/Uploads/Editor/2016-09-06/57ce310478786.png\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">项目周围配套完善，周边学区林立，各种生活设施一应俱全。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:center;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/Websites/zhongyu/Uploads/Editor/2016-09-06/57ce31c568447.png\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;本项目位于St Kilda Road 繁华商业街，被天然氧吧所包围。远眺飞利浦海湾，周围名校林立，各种商店、餐厅、休闲设施伸手可及，是体味墨尔本文化时尚精髓、共享南半球悠闲生活的绝佳选择。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:center;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/Websites/zhongyu/Uploads/Editor/2016-09-06/57ce3203b5d19.png\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;圣基尔达海滩(St Kilda Foreshore)是墨尔本最著名的海滨，游客可以选择在林荫大道上散步，或乘有轨电车从Fitzroy St出収，路经The Esplanade到达Acland St，一路上可尽情地欣赏当地丰富的文化生活。从F1赛道出来，没2分钟就是圣基尔达的主街-菲兹罗伊街。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:center;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/Websites/zhongyu/Uploads/Editor/2016-09-06/57ce327a1a658.png\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;楼盘对面是Albert Park,可以看整个公园的风景和F1比赛（18洞高尔夫球场兼澳大利亚一年一度的F1赛车主场地，另外在园内有个很大的人工湖）；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;楼盘位于450St,Kilda Road紧挨着的是Albert Park内的F1赛车道，所以该楼盘前方已无任何空地可建；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Albert Park隔壁的海滩上都是1-3层的别墅群，此楼盘高层医生还可以看到离City最近的海滩Hobsons Bay海景；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;该楼盘后面是St Kilda Road，距离约50米；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;距离约100米是电车站，7条电车通向名校以及CBD；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;几乎所有的墨尔本顶尖的公校、私校都坐落在该楼盘所在的区，项目离注明的St Kilda街50米，走路到Albert Park只需要1分钟；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;距离大型综合性公立医院The Alfred Hospital步行约5-10分钟（就在Wesley College隔壁）。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:center;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/Websites/zhongyu/Uploads/Editor/2016-09-06/57ce32ae22d7a.png\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:center;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"Default\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:center;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><img src=\"/Websites/zhongyu/Uploads/Editor/2016-09-06/57ce339d97bf1.png\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"Default\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"Default\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;采用顶尖设计，室内设计风格多元化。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"Default\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"Default\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:center;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/Websites/zhongyu/Uploads/Editor/2016-09-06/57ce348403651.png\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"Default\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;项目由知名开发商盛世集团血手国际一流设计师Bates Smart倾力打造。流畅的外观，华丽的曲线外形宛如一滴露珠，镶嵌在圣柯达绿荫丛中。全玻璃幕墙倒映着优美的自然景致，赋予现代的灵动之美，能够最大限度接受自然光的照射，外观通体闪耀，室内宽敞明亮。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"Default\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"Default\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:center;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/Websites/zhongyu/Uploads/Editor/2016-09-06/57ce35482dc87.png\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"Default\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"Default\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;项目融入高端酒店设计理念，宽敞人性化的户型设计，内饰纯粹典雅，舒适奢华，有多重配色方案可供选择，如沉稳深色系、优雅浅色系、经典色系等，供您多项选择。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"Default\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"Default\" style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<img src=\"/Websites/zhongyu/Uploads/Editor/2016-09-06/57ce33822f42b.png\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>', '', '11', '1');
INSERT INTO `xiaobing360_category` VALUES ('51', '', '网站建设', '', '3', '3', '1', '10', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'page_tongyong', '', '5', '2,3,7', '4', '0', '1', '1', '0', '0', '', '', '1473302895', '1494915815', '1', '465', '466', '467', '', '<p style=\"color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;text-align:center;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:1.333em;text-indent:2em;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#333333;\">企业网站的设计源于内容规划，企业做网站的内容</span>取决于经营特点与市场分析，而网站建设的技术，则是实现内容和设计的最终保障，三者相互依存，缺一不可。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;color:#535353;font-family:宋体;font-size:1.333em;text-indent:2em;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	因此，在网站策划阶段，我们会首先研究企业经营管理特点、网站运营目标，分析企业终端客户及市场状况，然后规划网站的内容与功能，根据网站的内容与功能再决定采用什么样的设计。最后，要实现符合网站需求的内容、功能与设计，我们还会规划稳定安全的技术方案做保障。\r\n</p>\r\n<img src=\"/Websites/zhongyu/Uploads/Editor/2017-05-16/591a9aa0e0b24.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', '', '11', '1');
